i\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor 唔識形容佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得1-2mm大，叫昆蟲好似太嚇鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0020b62783a3028980136849f6eae3cff42ba62f","tid":310200,"uid":52206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>卜泥的話去買紫色個款biokill<br />\nkeep住一兩個星期噴就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要清理曬佢地先噴？</blockquote><br />\n我自己係會直接噴 之後都會見唔到<br />\n但幾個月可能又會有番 <br />\n所以最好都係用除霉劑/油過哂<br />\n因為呢d多數發霉先有"},{"pid":"86c51f1dd68d12737e020f305b8b01acc4d3e825","tid":310200,"uid":102980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>卜泥的話去買紫色個款biokill<br />\nkeep住一兩個星期噴就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要清理曬佢地先噴？</blockquote><br />\n我自己係會直接噴 之後都會見唔到<br />\n但幾個月可能又會有番 <br />\n所以最好都係用除霉劑/油過哂<br />\n因為呢d多數發霉先有</blockquote><br />\n我屋企潮濕都出哂出黎<br />\n前排訓上隔床成日對住<br />\n我就淨係掃走佢地再用消毒酒精抹一次<br />\n有效幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5955115cc4f14220661884be750fc9c927cbe231","tid":310200,"uid":43580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>卜泥的話去買紫色個款biokill<br />\nkeep住一兩個星期噴就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要清理曬佢地先噴？</blockquote><br />\n我自己係會直接噴 之後都會見唔到<br />\n但幾個月可能又會有番 <br />\n所以最好都係用除霉劑/油過哂<br />\n因為呢d多數發霉先有</blockquote><br />\n好難斷尾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪叫卜泥？"},{"pid":"cee997d514448b31f233540d855ddcda0d0e3460","tid":310200,"uid":43580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>卜泥的話去買紫色個款biokill<br />\nkeep住一兩個星期噴就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要清理曬佢地先噴？</blockquote><br />\n我自己係會直接噴 之後都會見唔到<br />\n但幾個月可能又會有番 <br />\n所以最好都係用除霉劑/油過哂<br />\n因為呢d多數發霉先有</blockquote><br />\n我屋企潮濕都出哂出黎<br />\n前排訓上隔床成日對住<br />\n我就淨係掃走佢地再用消毒酒精抹一次<br />\n有效幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該有幾十隻 諗下自己晚晚訓係佢地下面<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}